FBIS3-31352 "dreeu033_y_94007" FBIS-EEU-94-033 Document Type:Daily Report 17 Feb 1994 YUGOSLAVIA Kosovo Police, Army Maltreat `Dozens' of Ethnic Albanians AU1602180294 Tirana TVSH Television Network in Albanian 1735 GMT 16 Feb 94 AU1602180294 Tirana TVSH Television Network Language: Albanian Article Type:BFN [Text] Reports from Prishtina confirm that recently the Serbian police and army have maltreated dozens of Albanian citizens who live in Morine near the Kosova-Albanian border area. The Serbian police repression has also been continuing in many villages in Podujeve. In Dyze in this commune, 17 Albanian homes have been raided.
